<Card title="Why Choose iTerm2?" icon={<Terminal className="h-5 w-5" />}>
The default macOS Terminal is functional, but iTerm2 offers significant improvements:

- ‚ú® Split panes (Cmd+D vertical, Cmd+Shift+D horizontal)
