- üîç Better search & autocomplete
- üé® Customizable triggers and profiles
- üéØ Improved color support
</Card>

<Steps>
<Step>
### Install iTerm2

```bash
brew install --cask iterm2
```
</Step>

<Step>
### Configure Key Settings

1. **Natural Text Editing**
   - Open iTerm2 Preferences
   - Navigate to Profiles ‚Üí Keys
   - Load Preset... ‚Üí Natural Text Editing

2. **Enable GPU Rendering**
   - Go to Advanced Settings
   - Search for "GPU"
